nodes.text: Senior Commander was a military rank used within the Imperial Security Bureau of the Galactic Empire. By the year 0 BBY, Alecia Beck held this title.

The rank was also used in the Chiss Ascendancy's Expansionary Defense Fleet, where Plikh'ar'illmorf served as Senior Commander aboard the Springhawk before and during Mitth'raw'nuruodo's mission to Batuu.
